name: Kill Bill Tarantino
description: Portrait of Director Quentin Tarantino in relation to his "fourth film", Kill Bill. Executed for the Village Voice, 2003. As research for this work, I was fortunate enough to enjoy a press screening with Mr. Tarantino. He screamed, gasped and clapped along with the rest of us for the entire film. The good old days. PNG 4,375 x 3,325 by @antiquefuture | justin wood
